Fix the misspelling of "parametrs" as "parameters" in
reclaim.rst and lru_sort.rst.

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/20260426231619.107231-3-sj@kernel.org
Signed-off-by: Cheng-Han Wu <hank20010209@gmail.com>
